OL,4,CPortugal's top art collector Joe
OL,5,CBerardo arrested over fraud allegations
OL,6, A prominent Portuguese businessman and
OL,7, art collector has been detained by
OL,8, police investigating fraud and money
OL,9, laundering allegations.
OL,11,FJoe Berardo was arrested on Tuesday as
OL,12,Fpolice raided several homes and banks.
OL,14,FMr Berardo, 76, is the founder of a
OL,15,Fmodern art museum - a major tourist
OL,16,Fattraction in the capital, Lisbon.
OL,18,FHe is accused of shifting valuable
OL,19,Fartworks into a trust to protect them
OL,20,Ffrom creditors. Mr Berardo has not
OL,21,Fcommented.
